{%- comment -%}
  Shipping Policy — Clear, friendly, no legalese.
  Standard 5-9 days, Express 3-7, Free over $100, Worldwide.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="policy-page shipping-page">
  <div class="policy-page__inner page-width">

    <span class="section-eyebrow">Shipping</span>
    <h1 class="section-heading">Shipping Policy</h1>
    <p class="policy-page__intro">We ship worldwide and want to make sure your [BRAND]™ belt gets to you as quickly and affordably as possible. Here's everything you need to know.</p>
    <p class="policy-page__updated">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>

    <div class="policy-content">

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Free Shipping</h2>
        <p>All orders over <strong>$100 USD</strong> qualify for <strong>free standard shipping</strong> — anywhere in the world. No coupon code needed. It's applied automatically at checkout.</p>
        <p>For orders under $100, a flat shipping fee will be calculated at checkout based on your location.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Shipping Options</h2>
        <div class="policy-table-wrap">
          <table class="policy-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Method</th>
                <th>Estimated Delivery</th>
                <th>Cost</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Standard Shipping</strong></td>
                <td>5–9 business days</td>
                <td>Free on orders over $100</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Express Shipping</strong></td>
                <td>3–7 business days</td>
                <td>Calculated at checkout</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="policy-note">Business days are Monday–Friday, excluding public holidays. Delivery times begin once your order has been processed and shipped (usually within 1–2 business days of placing your order).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Where We Ship</h2>
        <p>We ship to <strong>all countries worldwide</strong>, including the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, European Union, and beyond. If you can place an order on our site, we can deliver to your address.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Order Processing</h2>
        <p>Orders are typically processed within <strong>1–2 business days</strong>. Once your order ships, you'll receive a confirmation email with a tracking number so you can follow your package every step of the way.</p>
        <p>Orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed on the next business day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Tracking Your Order</h2>
        <p>Every order includes tracking. Once your order has shipped, you'll receive an email with your tracking number and a link to follow your package in real time. If you haven't received a tracking email within 3 business days of placing your order, please <a href="/pages/contact-us">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Customs & Duties (International Orders)</h2>
        <p>For international orders, please be aware that customs duties, taxes, or import fees may apply depending on your country's regulations. These charges are the responsibility of the buyer and are not included in our shipping costs. We recommend checking with your local customs office for more information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Lost or Damaged Packages</h2>
        <p>If your package appears to be lost in transit or arrives damaged, please <a href="/pages/contact-us">contact our support team</a> immediately. We'll work with the carrier to locate your package or send a replacement at no additional cost.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about shipping, don't hesitate to reach out. Email us at <strong>support@[brand].com</strong> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact Us</a> page. We're happy to help.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

